title: [PS3] PS3Ultimate CFW 4.50 v1.03-RazorX
description:
PlayStation 3 Homebrew Developer RazorX has released a 4.50CFW. This Custom Firmware features the usual patches found in most CFWs and then developer added alot of very nice cosmetic changes that consist of a replaced XMB Wave, Changed Startup message, New coldboot and sounds, Cleaning up of XMB Categories and more. Checkout all the details from RazorX below. 


Update: Oct. 12: RazorX has updated his CFW to version 1.03, see textfile for changes.
